{
  "stem": "10699.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Everybody was on the march.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But you mustn't forget that the Italians were also our enemies, and therefore, they were bombarding us on the way down.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we-- we were running.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were-- from the beginning of June, we were running down, and the Germans were following us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They were behind us, the army.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we reached-- by the time we reached-- that was [NON-ENGLISH], the Germans had caught up with us.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So we--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were behind us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were being bombarded.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had sometimes to run from the lorry, and run into the forest, the nearest place where we could hide, and then go back again.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And by the time we reached that little village, the Germans had-- had reached our-- our place and were going forward towards Vichy.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So at that time, we-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] the commandant of the-- in that village said that all men aged from 18 to 45 should go to Vichy to be recruited.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So the people-- I was very ill at the time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had caught tonsillitis.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- but we had to go on to Vichy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when we arrived in Vichy, somehow nobody found the place where you're supposed to be recruited, so we just watched what was going on.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You see, the Germans had reached, now, Vichy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were emptying the shops.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, all the lovely-- the goods that they could find, either they took it or they paid for it, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But they were-- they were buying, or they were looting, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we could see that wasn't the place to stay, because they were all in Vichy.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my father decided that we should really continue, and we shouldn't stay in Vichy.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
